樓上，40%樓下？<br />\n<br />\n下下講價先㩒低個息？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個個借到record爛哂先搵財仔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLoan既話唔太清楚，聽講無3，40%咁高，年利率廿幾%到啦，根據每個人既財務紀錄會有唔同<br />\n<br />\n可能我做個間都算比較大，批loan其實都唔算鬆手"},{"pid":"a3387325028ab383b8bd1d472a7190df73b96d56","tid":40841,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"唔還錢係咪會淋人紅油？"},{"pid":"e509c0fed6aa4cc324f0432be4d15ebe987f07c6","tid":40841,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔還錢係咪會淋人紅油？</blockquote><br />\n呢d野係收數工司做唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n不過d contract寫到明如果唔還錢唔排除將你d資料比收數公司....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b161bb2d84c1f64ad1aac6b0c9be9fcabee6289","tid":40841,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪次次開價個息口都30%樓上，40%樓下？<br />\n<br />\n下下講價先㩒低個息？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個個借到record爛哂先搵財仔？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLoan既話唔太清楚，聽講無3，40%咁高，年利率廿幾%到啦，根據每個人既財務紀錄會有唔同<br />\n<br />\n可能我做個間都算比較大，批loan其實都唔算鬆手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過申請大眾財務借五萬要還七萬（24月），差唔多成40%，痴撚線，同佢講話恒生借咗俾我啦咁，轉個頭又話幫我爭取到優惠利率，借五萬還五萬五，差幾撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾都係乜都冇借過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c59664f65f1cfd92e84f0487d1990043aef06d0","tid":40841,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔還錢係咪會淋人紅油？</blockquote><br />\n呢d野係收數工司做唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n不過d contract寫到明如果唔還錢唔排除將你d資料比收數公司....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工你老母"},{"pid":"36aeb9bf8f4655339123f5e338f8686c56c47a8f","tid":40841,"uid":65330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-1